Simple Video surveillance App
===============================
1.Restricted area Monitering 
2.Specified Object Tracking Problem in an Environment of Multiple Moving Objects


S/W  Requirement 
=================
OpenCV 2.4.9
	

How to execute the program
==========================

	2 steps of Application this 
	============================
	1.Run selected region (generated the .xml file)
	2.Give Video input




1. goto the Select_Region floder and  run this 

g++ *.cpp -o selectregion `pkg-config --cflags --libs opencv`
./selectregion

**********left click for draw polylines , right click for end ********

2. goto the Restricted_area floder and run this

g++ *.cpp -o rarea `pkg-config --cflags --libs opencv`
./rarea -v ../data/pedestrian_detection.avi


while running
************** u can track Specified Object using mouse click (draw rect)******








